t of you with the pearl to saela@eqdrinal.com prior to being added. There are NO EXCEPTIONS to this rule. Along with the pearl screenshot, you should also send in (1) your e-mail address, (2) your guild's name, and (3) a list of persons who may be contacted if you are not online. The clerics who are currently on the list must send in this information to maintain their position on the list.<br><br>3. Always have someone in the RF camp, whether it be you or your representative. Anyone in the RF camp should refer clerics seeking to be added to the list to this forum.<br><br>4. There is a 3 hour time limit from the moment Ragefire spawns for the first cleric on the list to kill him, during which time other forces are welcome to gather and prepare, but not engage Ragefire. If the first cleric on the list does not kill Ragefire in this time, the list's integrity should continue to be maintained by going through the list in order until a cleric who is online is in the zone and ready. Ragefire is never FFA -- after three hours, that spawn belongs to the highest listed cleric prepared for an engagement.<br><br>5. Post here immediately after you have killed RF so that the next person on the list is notified.<br><br>6. Those clerics with * in front of their name have sent in their screenshots showing them with the pearl from Sol B.<br><br><br>This list was created to maintain civility among the guilds of Drinal. The current listing is:<br><br>1 ramor (Winter's Light)<br>2 *fierire (Undivided Faith)<br>3 *feelsgood (Dark Family)<br>4 chindra (Unconquered)<br>5 castiron<br>6 *funno (Guardians of the Keep)<br>7 exidus<br>8 callandra (removed on request)<br>9 koll (Bushido Clain)<br>10 *saela (The Kindred)<br>11 dolphine (Undivided Faith)<br>12 *laline <br>13 *Gigelat (Guardians of the Keep) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/usaelavee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saela Vee</A> at: 6/1/02 11:09:03 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFF